WEBVTT

1
00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:59.640 
他看上去就是这种人
He looks like a pajama man.

2
00:05:59.810 --> 00:06:01.580 
穿熨好的条纹睡衣
Striped and ironed.

3
00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:07.670 
他和你说什么了
And? What did he have to say?

4
00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:12.250 
他请求我同意他打破我们之间的约定
He asked my permission to break our pact.

5
00:06:12.250 --> 00:06:14.380 
约定  什么约定
Pact? What pact?

6
00:06:15.050 --> 00:06:16.770 
我们说好了如果我们俩不能结婚
We promised that if we couldn't marry each other,

7
00:06:16.770 --> 00:06:18.180 
也不会和其他人结婚
we'd never marry anyone else.

8
00:06:18.180 --> 00:06:19.700 
我懂了
Ah, I see.

9
00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:21.110 
他
Well...

10
00:06:22.350 --> 00:06:26.230 
他现在想不再受这项约定的束缚
he now wishes to be released from that pledge.

11
00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.880 
准备结婚吗
To get married?

